&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#09f;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# Try to get the emulator cert in a loop&lt;/span&gt;
